:"Arthur de Chevauchesul родился в 1085 г. в местности татворт, сомирсет, Англия. Он женился на женщине по имени Matilda d'Oiley около 1115 г. в местности тецворт, оксфордшир, Англия, Великобритания. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Он умер в 1120 г. в местности оксфордшир, Англия, Великобритания в возрасте 35 лет."},"sm":{"1085–1120":"1085–1120","1089–1141":"1089–1141","1116–1145":"1116–1145","1106":"1106","1116":"1116","1145":"1145","1089":"1089","about 1115":"e tusa o le 1115","1120":"1120","1086":"1086","1141":"1141","1085":"1085","1096":"1096","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, Egelani","Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England":"Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, Egelani, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"1085–1120":"1085–1120","1089–1141":"1089–1141","1116–1145":"1116–1145","1106":"1106","1116":"1116","1145":"1145","1089":"1089","about 1115":"okolo 1115","1120":"1120","1086":"1086","1141":"1141","1085":"1085","1096":"1096","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, England","Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England":"Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo"},"es":{"1085–1120":"1085–1120","1089–1141":"1089–1141","1116–1145":"1116–1145","1106":"1106","1116":"1116","1145":"1145","1089":"1089","about 1115":"aproximadamente 1115","1120":"1120","1086":"1086","1141":"1141","1085":"1085","1096":"1096","Tatworth, Chard, Somerset, England":"Tatworth, Somerset, Inglaterra","Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, England":"Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, Inglaterra, Reino Unido","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, Inglaterra, Reino Unido","lifeSummary":"Arthur de Chevauchesul nació en 1085, en Tatworth, Somerset, Inglaterra. Se casó con Matilda d'Oiley aproximadamente 1115, en Tetsworth, Oxfordshire, Inglaterra, Reino Unido. Fueron padres de por lo menos 1 hijo. Murió en 1120, en Oxfordshire, Inglaterra, Reino Unido, a la edad de 35 años."},"sv":{"1085–1